{
  "id": "crate-secretsx-lj8",
  "title": "workspace: CI, docs, release infrastructure",
  "description": "Set up workspace-level quality gates and release automation. CI jobs: cargo fmt --all (fail on diff); typos on all src/; cargo clippy --all-features -p <crate> -- -D warnings for each crate; cargo hack check --feature-powerset --no-dev-deps on the umbrella; RUSTDOCFLAGS='--cfg docsrs -D warnings' cargo +nightly doc --no-deps --all-features; cargo test on each crate. Integration test jobs: LocalStack for AWS backends; vault Docker image for hashicorp-vault; softhsm2 for pkcs11; wolfHSM simulator for wolfhsm; credential-gated jobs for bitwarden/doppler. Release: all crates in workspace published together, workspace.version bumped in lockstep.",
